83
00:08:05,038 --> 00:08:05,956
<i>Twelve months.</i>

84
00:08:07,249 --> 00:08:09,209
<i>Can I keep up an exercise that long?</i>

85
00:08:23,723 --> 00:08:26,517
<i>When I read these words,
