425
00:31:26,078 --> 00:31:29,498
Balq Industries, Balq Energy,
Balq Paper, Balq Peanuts...

426
00:31:29,582 --> 00:31:30,499
Why?

427
00:31:31,125 --> 00:31:34,670
Well, it's all about the reconsecration.

428
00:31:34,754 --> 00:31:37,297
